  Locus:
    Page: 122
    Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Enemy
---
Emotion, whether of ridicule, anger, or sorrow, whether used at a puppet
show, a funeral, or a battle, is your grandest of levelers. The man who
would always be superior should be always apathetic.
